{"tid":1187830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[69兵法] 排陣+策略 *習近平權鬥*","createTime":"2019-06-06T01:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T22:20:35.000Z","uid":61281,"like":172,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a48662bfe09e9bcab37a3e40580f0eb8129a70ad","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">習近平為奪權剷除政敵薄熙來</span></span><br />\n<br />\n*對峙情況適用*<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">N國聯軍~聯合國passport兵團</span></strong></span><br />\n外藉港人義士行先保護港台中兄弟<br />\n排陣次序：西方N國&gt;港=台&gt;中<br />\n體力次序：強壯&gt;&gt;&gt;弱小<br />\n(於人群中鳩叫: 誰有passport! 即隨時流動變陣) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1baQJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1baQJ.png&h=87b9ed11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n       <br />\n           <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺國際記者與全世界觀察之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防暴警到底會用幾大武力衝擊聯合國軍呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">支持薄熙來越獄奪權取代習近平成國家主席</span></span>"},{"pid":"25c5d62876bc19c46d117186c2faca9553257723","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>世界各國！<br />\n抗絕分化！<br />\n團結一致！<br />\n唯一敵人！<br />\n中國共狗！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n終於明白歷史文宣嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643a8d3c9d96340cb45acb6db0c81d0519317741","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"By浴火重生火鳳凰<br />\n<br />\n要對抗五毛分化技倆，首先自己要先拚棄批評其他同路人所做出嘅行為，同路人係指任何反共力量（包括泛民），而唔包括返工不了/ 遊行有乜用？（消極撚）/ 散播負面情緒嘅分化撚五毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設如果你想衝但面對人地係和理非嘅立場，唔好鬧人，相反如果你係和理非但面對人地係想衝嘅立場，亦都唔好鬧人甚至阻人，否則會破壞大家關係從而削弱反共力量<br />\n<br />\n再強調一次，要杜絕五毛分化，首先自己要先拚棄批評其他同路人所做出嘅行為，至於唔同門派之間嘅舊仇恨，宜家大敵當前兵臨城下，都唔好互踩住（eg黃毓民、陳雲甚至熱狗之流，雖然我都覺得熱狗好賤格，但只要冇人彩佢無理佢就可以，冇必要鬧戰）否則五毛好易利用呢點製造缺口挑撥「土本vs泛民」嘅關係，造成反共力量嘅內亂"},{"pid":"b1f7c7c637c38d43770418e456cd0ae73c9baafd","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":57,"dislike":4,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"高權限五毛行為人士<br />\n(可quote和貼中共黨政權鬥內容)<br />\n<br />\nElend_Venture #1751<br />\n孖寶契弟 #8605<br />\n霍金轉身 #27866<br />\n牙古路(有養狗) #5649<br />\n一齊攬炒 #33874<br />\n我只是個孩子 #35420<br />\n布丁火鍋 #39706<br />\nBrahim_Diaz #40757<br />\n不可說嗎 #59503<br />\nSeolhyun #89931<br />\nMy火柴女孩 #247836<br />\n寶玉BB #249885<br />\n哇啦哈哈哈 #251665"},{"pid":"810e3463b608689a67ac2873b3e4b0754ee5fb1b","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆共狗個臭街唔好當我地流</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03f7e22f8025c61012b2a35f165e498dfb2b818","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"中國藉=/=共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f55085a8b69d2cb4b4f4acf39333a977a280477","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fb42a5a8bd9718b6ba3d0784dc6c7950fbe34d","tid":1187830,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f0b56f7f9e84fe7e